Storyline

Raymond has a prestigious MBA, but he can't find work. He 
can channel the paranormal, but chatting with a cute girl 
mystifies him. Kicked out of his big city apartment, Raymond 
returns home to his overbearing mother, ex-jock father, 
and beer-bellied classmates. But when a vengeful ghost 
terrorizes the small town, the city-boy recruits Becca,
 a badass local bartender, to solve the mystery of the 
spirit threatening everyone's lives.
